      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "VELOCITY YIN (1) showed good pace from out wide and was prominent early but began to paddle and faded out of it when 7th at Capalaba in Grade 4/5 company. Has ability and can bounce back. REDMAN JOHNNY (6) turned spotting a big start finishing fourth (26.00) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. In the mix. SWEET LADETTE (8) has some solid form under her belt and proved too classy last time to win by a nose at Q Straight in a handy 19.10 beating Ellen Rose. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Must be included in calculations. ON THE WHISPER (3) can return to form after missing the top-three at this circuit last time out.",
